David M. GliklichManaging DirectorSan Francisco (Real Estate)Mr. Gliklich joined us in 2005. Previously, Mr. Gliklich worked as a financial analyst at Goldman Sachs in the real estate investment banking group. Mr. Gliklich graduated cum laude from Harvard College with an A.B. in Chemistry.

Charles GunawanManaging DirectorSingaporeMr. Gunawan joined us in 2012 and is a Managing Director at Farallon Capital Asia Pte. Ltd. Prior to joining, Mr. Gunawan was a Managing Director and Co-Head of the investment banking division of Credit Suisse Indonesia. Prior to Credit Suisse, Mr. Gunawan was a Managing Director in the investment banking division of Goldman Sachs Singapore, where he focused on origination and execution of advisory and financing deals in Indonesia. Mr. Gunawan graduated from Universitas Indonesia with a Bachelor’s degree in Mechanical Engineering, and from UCLA Anderson School of Management with an M.B.A.

Stephen P. HeathManaging DirectorSan Francisco (Real Estate)Mr. Heath joined us in 1998. Prior to joining Farallon, Mr. Heath was Vice President at Hearthstone Advisors, a large investor of institutional capital in the single-family home building business. Mr. Heath graduated from the University of Denver with a B.A. in History.

