Philipp StreppManaging DirectorLondonMr. Strepp joined us in 2007 and is a Member of Farallon Capital Europe LLP. Prior to joining, Mr. Strepp worked as an associate in the corporate finance department of JPMorgan’s European financial institutions group. Mr. Strepp graduated from the University of St. Gallen, Switzerland, with an M.S. in Management & Finance.

