Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 1:15 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C. is a privately owned hedge fund manager. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to institutions including college endowments, charitable foundations and pension plans, and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public and private debt and equity securities market across the globe with a focus on developed and emerging markets alike. It employs strategies such as credit investments, long/short equity, merger arbitrage, real estate-related investments, and direct Investments. The firm employ val...
Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C. is a privately owned hedge fund manager. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to institutions including college endowments, charitable foundations and pension plans, and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public and private debt and equity securities market across the globe with a focus on developed and emerging markets alike. It employs strategies such as credit investments, long/short equity, merger arbitrage, real estate-related investments, and direct Investments. The firm employ value driven approach with a combination of fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach. It employs a combination of in-house and external research to make its investments. The firm seeks to make direct investments in private companies specializing in recapitalization and special situations; and real estate including office, retail, multifamily, and industrial assets. Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C. was founded in March 1986 and is based in San Francisco, California.
Detailed Description


